    "Title": "Combat Gauntlet - Scenario #3",
    "Description": "Congrats on completing part two of this eight-part course.   \n\nThe third scenario throws tactical considerations into the mix. This time around the attacking ships are from distinct classes with distinct battlefield applications. Knowing what targets to prioritize is vital to surviving engagements against multiple ships.      \n\nWhenever you\u2019re ready, head to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> to get started.\n\nAs a bonus, successful completion of the scenario will net the original contractor holder an award of <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) MG Scrip</EM4>.\n\nTRICKS OF THE TRADE:\n- Bigger They Are \u2013 Try to evaluate which threat is the most dangerous and take them out first.\n- Shields \u2013 If you\u2019re taking a lot of damage, don\u2019t be afraid to boost away and let your shields regenerate.\n\nGood luck out there, \nInstructor Gilly     \n\n\nABOUT GILLY\u2019S FLIGHT SCHOOL  \nInstructor Lucas \u201cGilly\u201d Baramsco has served in six squadrons and has over ten years of teaching experience. Whether a student with zero flight experience or a professional looking to polish their skills, Gilly Flight School offers a variety of courses to \u201cLaunch Your Piloting Career.\u201d",
